          "reviewBody": "One of the best school in the city. They have good values and approach for education. This is the future of education. They handle children with a good grace and children love and enjoy what they learn. What more can a parent expect from a school. We can see the amazing transformation for our children once u enroll in the school. Their thought process and culture changes in a good approach. Thanks to Sudha Mahesh Aunty for taking this idea of HLC community.",
          "publisher": {
