            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "The school looks Amazing.. very modern look still they have traditional aspects.. very spacious.. very big school with big football ground and two basketball grounds.. located in a calm area.. school looks good interms of infrastructure.. am an outsider and none of known person studies here. So I did not review about teaching, fees and related aspects. But I can say this school imparts very good values among young minds.. for example nature based ventilation system, garbage collection system, importance on games,  etc.. Good..  surrounded by trees.. kids will love this school..",
          "publisher": {
